# Chapter 1: Machine Learning Lifecycle

## What is the Machine Learning Lifecycle?

The Machine Learning (ML) Lifecycle is the complete process of building, deploying, and maintaining a machine learning model.

It starts with identifying a business problem and ends with continuously monitoring and improving the deployed model.

The lifecycle ensures that machine learning solutions remain accurate, reliable, and useful over time.

